04:17.622 --> 04:20.041
Would you like one?

04:20.125 --> 04:23.378
Damn it all. Can I- Give me some money.
I need to get some popcorn.

04:23.461 --> 04:27.674
- You got money.
- I asked for your money.

04:27.757 --> 04:30.051
What do you say?

04:30.135 --> 04:32.387
Cheap ass.

04:32.470 --> 04:35.974
- Thank you.
- Come on.

04:36.057 --> 04:38.101
Cat got your tongue?

04:38.184 --> 04:41.479
You know, I don't even know you,
and I dislike you already.

04:52.282 --> 04:54.201
Come on!

04:56.453 --> 04:58.371
- Hey, we're sold out.
- Oh, cool!

05:01.124 --> 05:03.043
Hello.

05:03.126 --> 05:08.882
Hi. Um, can I have a medium popcorn,
no butter, and a small diet Pepsi?

05:08.965 --> 05:10.884
- You got it.
- Thanks.

05:10.967 --> 05:12.886
That's it. I am not
going back in there.

05:12.969 --> 05:15.138
Come on, you chickenshit.
It's just a movie.

05:15.180 --> 05:17.390
No, it's not just a movie.
It's a true story.

05:17.474 --> 05:19.643
All these kids got killed
a couple years ago in California.

05:19.684 --> 05:22.312
- Here's the popcorn.
- Thanks.

05:22.354 --> 05:25.899
I was so scared,
I almost had a heart attack.

05:25.982 --> 05:28.777
Hah!
Stab you, man!

05:38.328 --> 05:40.247
- Whoa!

05:43.833 --> 05:46.836
- You ass!
- I'm sorry. I had to, baby.

05:46.878 --> 05:50.090
- What are you playing?
- Would you relax?

05:50.173 --> 05:52.092
God! What's wrong with you?

05:52.175 --> 05:54.844
I don't like being scared.
I don't like that.

05:54.928 --> 05:57.722
Baby, it's just
a movie.

05:57.764 --> 06:00.684
Besides, scary movies
are great foreplay.

06:00.725 --> 06:03.436
Excuse me?

06:03.520 --> 06:05.480
Let's go see
Sandra Bullock.

06:05.564 --> 06:10.402
Oh, no. Sandra started already.
We can stay.

06:10.485 --> 06:12.571
Just stop playin' so much.

06:16.116 --> 06:18.994
All right. I gotta go
to the bathroom.

06:20.453 --> 06:22.414
See ya inside.

07:30.440 --> 07:32.359
Sorry.

07:35.153 --> 07:37.113
Hello?

08:50.604 --> 08:53.732
No, no, no, no, no, no!
Don't do that!

09:00.113 --> 09:02.908
Move! Move!
Go!

09:02.991 --> 09:04.910
All right, go!

09:10.040 --> 09:12.209
Baby, give it up.

09:14.544 --> 09:16.838
You came back just in time.
It looks like she's about to get it.

09:16.922 --> 09:18.840
Want some popcorn?

09:23.595 --> 09:25.931
Uh-uh. See, if that was me,
I would be out of there.

09:32.312 --> 09:35.065
Oh!
Here it comes!

09:35.106 --> 09:38.235
- Here it comes!

09:38.318 --> 09:40.403
Here it comes!
Oh, my God!

11:44.694 --> 11:47.572
Whoa, oh, oh

